data.description: This charming home is what you've always dreamed of! The moment you walk into the open foyer adorned with wood floors and classy accented finishes, you will fall in love! This home is loaded with beautiful features such as crown molding, stainless steel appliances, an extended balcony, an inviting front porch with double glass doors, and lush landscaping all around the property! This home features 4 spacious bedrooms, 2 and a half baths, a formal living and dining room, a breakfast area, a spacious den, an exquisite sunroom, and a study/flex room. Both baths come with double vanity sinks and the primary bathroom has 2 spacious closets! Come see this unique beauty for yourself and make it your forever home!
